snippet.title: The Reel Rejects
snippet.description:
The Reel Rejects are the first people to ever put a spin on the word "Real" with the spelling of "Reel" - NO ONE HAS EVER DONE THIS!

We got Trailer Reactions, Movie Reviews, Movie Chat (News, Spoiler Reviews, Film Rumors), Sketches, Youtube Video Reactions, and podcasts plus guests throughout the month!!!!!

ENJOY THE CHANNEL!

Lead Host, Main Editor, & Producer: Greg Alba
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/thegregalba/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/thegregalba

Co-Host, Co-Editor: John Humphrey
Twitter: https://twitter.com/datjohnhumphrey
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/datjohnhumphrey/

Reel Rejects Social Media:
FB: https://www.facebook.com/TheReelRejects/
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/reelrejects/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/thereelrejects

If you'd like to help support the channel, check out our Patreon Page!
https://www.patreon.com/thereelrejects

Based Out In Los Angeles, Calfornia!

Logo Designed By James Boland http://www.Instagram.com/nalbis
